    <link href="/2020/10/19/%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
    <url>/2020/10/19/%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>调试信息</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="打印练习格式控制出现的小问题"><a href="#打印练习格式控制出现的小问题" class="headerlink" title="打印练习格式控制出现的小问题"></a>打印练习格式控制出现的小问题</h3><p>偶然运行之前写的练手题目<br><img src="/img/strange_tri.jpg" alt="a"></p><blockquote><p>由于占据格子的问题，当数据大于9的时候，会出现排版上的问题<br>好吧算是小问题，但是细看之下发现了另外一个大问题，第一行的1怎么不见了(特地加了个–&gt;指出来)</p></blockquote><p>分析代码唯一的区别，大于9的时候会执行</p><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(n&lt;<span class="hljs-number">0</span>||n&gt;<span class="hljs-number">9</span>)   &#123;       <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;The num must between 1 to 9!&quot;</span>);   &#125;</code></pre><hr><h4 id="分析下产生的原因"><a href="#分析下产生的原因" class="headerlink" title="分析下产生的原因"></a>分析下产生的原因</h4><blockquote><p>在看到输出前已经有printf且没有换行之后，加上”\n”进行换行问题解决了</p></blockquote><h5 id="更深层次测原因"><a href="#更深层次测原因" class="headerlink" title="更深层次测原因"></a>更深层次测原因</h5><hr><p>格式控制.c</p><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">pyramid</span><span class="hljs-params">( <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n )</span></span>;<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n;    <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n);    pyramid(n);    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;&#125;<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">pyramid</span><span class="hljs-params">( <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n)</span></span><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span>  pos=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span>  prenull=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span>  num=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(n&lt;<span class="hljs-number">0</span>||n&gt;<span class="hljs-number">9</span>)    &#123;        <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;The num must between 1 to 9!&quot;</span>);    &#125;    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(pos=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;pos&lt;n+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;pos++)    &#123;        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(prenull=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;prenull&lt;=n-pos;prenull++)        &#123;            <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span>);        &#125;        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(num=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;num&lt;=pos;num++)        &#123;            <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d &quot;</span>,pos);        &#125;       <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>);    &#125;&#125;</code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
